matches_found.targetFile: 029 Eating & Confused Trying To Use Food To Heal_jwdnltN8WM0_en_auto.txt

video.title: 029 Eating & Confused: Trying To Use Food To Heal
video.description:
Do we listen to our body? Or are we just listening to our consciousness? Is our consciousness conditioned to choose the foods our body doesn’t want to eat? Does our body want the same foods our consciousness wants? No one should be judged upon what they are eating. In today’s harsh world it’s easy to lean on comfort foods and use them as a drug to get by. At the same time, we kind of are aware that our body really doesn’t want ice cream, chicken fingers, cheesy pasta, cheeseburgers, pizza, and chocolate. And what about our stomachs, do our stomachs want the same choices of food we want? Do our stomachs want beer and barbecue, chicken wings, cakes and cookies, donuts, macaroni and cheese, crab cakes and tuna fish sandwiches? Do our stomachs understand the term moderation and what our brainwashed conception of moderation is?
Let’s face it, there is a huge disconnect between our mind and body, and many people go through life believing that their body is telling them what it really wants when it comes to food and drink. People often think about what they need, but don’t realize it may not be what their stomach or body needs, and yet their stomach and body have no option but to live with the choices of the mind and consciousness of that person. Even then, that person’s choice in food may be what they are told to choose, especially by others in the realm of health, who are also recommending foods they think the body needs, and they themselves are in the same situation as the people they are recommending to. Everyone is stuck in a cycle of not knowing what their body wants or needs. Listen to this gripping episode about our digestion and how food works inside of our gut.

matches_found.originalFile: 039 Microdosing Psychedelics - What Goes Wrong_TzM2S3A3xPU_en_auto.txt
matches_found.targetFile: 039 Microdosing & Psychedelics What Goes Wrong_TzM2S3A3xPU_en_auto.txt

video.title: 039 Microdosing & Psychedelics: What Goes Wrong
video.description:
When we hear the words Micro-Dosing, a trending term, something happens in our mind: it draws a person in, it’s mysterious yet sounds scientific. The word “dose” holds power—it’s a word that has its own energetic force as if it’s alive. How is it alive? It’s an old word that the pharmaceutical world adopted, and the word is etched into generations of people. It’s instilled deep within the consciousness of the human mind and soul.

Around the word dose, there is fear. Fear stems from taking too much of something that isn’t normally good for us and even could be dangerous to us. A large dose of anything can be scary and even concerning. This is why prescription drugs have strict guidelines from medical authorities. Too big of a dose of a drug could mean overdosing, which is also a word deep in the consciousness of so many.

There is a party culture out there in this world. It’s a mindset that’s also ingrained in so many. Many people believe they need a stimulant of some kind to power them through life, or they feel they need something to relax them, and many people are struggling with symptoms and conditions, and are even suffering greatly with both mental and physical pain, so drinking and taking recreational drugs are on the rise. It’s unhealthy and toxic to the physical body and brain and has injured millions of people in various ways. Someone always knows someone that eventually had a close call or experience that wasn’t pleasing.

Microdosing has become a trend due to its seemingly controlled nature, an illusion that whatever you are partaking in is safe and even scientifically monitored in some way. It’s a way to lower fear and drive interest because how can something be toxic to you if it’s in such a small dosage. 

Get ready for a truly informative and enlightening episode—the truth about Microdosing.

For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com

video.title: 095 Geoengineering: Spraying Chemtrails
video.description:
Geoengineering is an umbrella term for protecting the planet from catastrophic conditions that lead to elevations of temperatures resulting from pollution and climate change, and to other inconsistencies of weather change. However, the Geoengineering umbrella term comes with mystery and sinister activity that puts the world at great harm and risk. The sad part is, there’s much more to Geoengineering than recently understood and talked about. Public authorities that are awakening to white streaks in the sky are still very much in the dark as to the level of evil within the plan to spray not just our skies here in the U.S., but every sky around the globe. Who’s funding these mysterious programs, where are they getting the resources for equipment, and how many jet planes are being deployed every day to carry out one of the greatest deceptions and scams of all time, the Geoengineering and Chemtrailing mission? In this first episode of a series dedicated to Geoengineering and chemtrails, you will begin a journey of learning the ins and outs of what’s in the sky that’s harmful and how to protect you and your loved ones. Becoming an expert at what’s around us is truly empowering…
 
In this episode…

Learn about how the Great Powers that run this world are in control of geoengineering.

Discover what secret missions are occurring up in the sky every minute of every day all over the globe.

Uncover how and why our atmosphere is being altered.

Learn about how some public officials in the U.S. are trying to change the laws surrounding geoengineering.

Discover if geoengineering planes are different than chemtrail planes, and where these planes are taking off and landing from.

Uncover the cost behind geoengineering.

Learn which chemicals are being released into the atmosphere and for what purposes.
 
All this and more, tune in and don’t miss out on this important episode. You can revisit this episode anytime you need it.
 
For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com

DAY 14
Pharmaceutical Exposure
Brain Shot Therapy Challenge

Some medications can be useful in crisis situations, such as injuries or severe infections. There are times when they are truly necessary. Pharmaceuticals can affect the functions of the brain in ways that aren’t always ideal. That is, there are side effects, sometimes debilitating and life-altering and even creating a dependency that outweighs the original problem for which the person took the medication. Long-term use of pharmaceuticals can end up saturating brain tissue and dampening the central nervous system’s ability to perform, and pharmaceutical exposure happens without us even knowing it, such as through our water and food supply and parks. 

The Medical Medium Pharmaceutical Exposure Brain Shot from Brain Saver and Brain Saver Protocols, Cleanses & Recipes is formulated for exposure to prescribed or over-the-counter medications or other pharmaceuticals, whether on a one-time or continual basis.

video.title: Disease - Wild Blueberries Vs Cultivated Blueberries
video.description:
Disease – Wild Blueberries Vs Cultivated

Stock Up & Save – Get $20 Off a Case of Twelve Wyman’s Wild Blueberry Juice at https://bit.ly/38cMfvd

Cultivated blueberries and wild blueberries are not the same thing, and therefore effect 
people differently. Cultivated blueberries are weak. Cultivated doesn’t have the same antioxidant or phytochemical compound strength or that adaptogenic power that wild blueberries have. The cultivated blueberry has not been around for thousands of years, it’s a spin-off of its cousin the wild blueberry. A wild blueberry can survive on its own through droughts, frozen tundra, floods, freeze and fire. There are hundreds 
and hundreds of different varieties of wild blueberries within the same crop of wild 
blueberries, they are not just one strain, so it can’t be wiped out as easily or at all by disease as the cultivated blueberry can.

I stand behind Wyman’s mission with this juice so much that I am working with 
Wyman’s to keep this medicinal drink available. From now through Wednesday,

video.title: B12 For Your Brain, Soul & Intuition
video.description:
Join me live to discover why B12 is such an important nutrient, not only for our brains and physical wellbeing, but emotionally and spiritually too. memory, mood, heart, energy, and more, but there is so much more to understand about how this special vitamin works with our soul to ignite our intuitive, psychic, telepathic, and clairvoyant skills. This is what I’ll be talking about on today’s live, plus so much more. 

When it comes to B12, it’s important to know that not every B12 supplement is helpful. In truth, many B12 supplements contain ingredients I don’t recommend, like citric acid or natural and artificial flavors. Then there’s the form of B12 a supplement offers. They aren’t all the same. For example, many B12 supplements contain cyanocobalamin, which is a form of B12 I don’t recommend.

My preferred form of B12 is a blend of methycobalamin and adenosylcobalamin. Vimergy B12 is my favorite B12 supplement because it contains the right kinds of B12, with the right quality, proportions, and clean ingredients–there’s no citric acid, alcohol, artificial flavors, natural flavors, low-quality glycerin, corn, soy, gluten or GMOs. I fully endorse Vimergy supplements because I love the quality, cleanliness, and efficacy of their products. I am working with Vimergy because it’s so important to get truly beneficial supplements out to the people who need them. I consider Vimergy Organic B12 to be a foundational supplement and I personally take it every day. 

My Favorite B12 : https://bit.ly/3xoGT9z

video.title: 018 Blood Draw: Bloodletting & Vampirism
video.description:
Many people battling symptoms, conditions, or chronic illness are subjected to routine blood draws and tests. How can these routine blood draws affect the body? 

In this episode, I uncover important truths about blood draws and reveal why the blood testing and donation system is broken and outdated. I explain how blood testing affects the immune system and why this can be dangerous, especially for the chronically ill. Find out how to determine the amount needed when getting your blood drawn and tested, and learn how much of your blood is discarded and wasted, and how very little of your blood is used for the testing process. Listen as I share what variables should be considered before getting a blood test and how gender can affect these variables. I cover what to ask for from your doctor when it comes to getting your blood tested and how best to protect yourself before and after a blood draw or blood donation.

To learn more, visit medicalmedium.com

video.title: 070 Problematic & Damaging Supplements: Deer Antler, Diatomaceous Earth, Essential Oils & More
video.description:
Everyone believes in essential oils as being helpful in some ways. This is true; essential oils can be helpful, but used in the wrong way can do the opposite. This is just one of the many supplements that people use on a daily basis that can have a negative impact on one’s health. Diatomaceous Earth has gained popularity as a fix-all for many problems related to health, but there is a dark side to that as well. So many are desperate for a quick fix that they run to any trend that gets placed before them. It’s a bear-eats-bear world of selling off anything and everything as a miracle fix for today’s problems. And then there are Creature Parts—they have become more popular than ever lately. Consuming a number of Creature Parts is also gaining steam because people still, to this day, think they can fix an organ by eating an organ. Get ready for this episode—you won’t be disappointed. We are covering some of the most deceiving trick-outs in the health industry.

Listen to this advertisement-free podcast on Apple & Spotify.

In this episode…
• Discover what you’re ingesting that could be harmful to your health.
• Learn what Creature Parts are and how can they be purposefully misleading.
• Learn about collagen, whale meat, colostrum and other supplements and what impact these can have upon ingestion.
• Uncover how the hormones in deer antler affect your body and your own hormones.
• Discover in what ways Diatomaceous Earth can be a trigger.
• Uncover the truth about digestive bitters and how it’s not so different from consuming alcohol.
• Learn what specific symptoms can be associated with a sensitive central nervous system and how Essential Oils can impact this.

All this and more, tune in and don’t miss out on this important episode. You can revisit this episode anytime you need it.

For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com

video.title: Food Fear   Are Your Health Symptoms Giving You An Eating Disorder
video.description:
When we get health symptoms, many times we associate those symptoms with the foods we are eating. When a symptom comes we question why is this problem here now? What is wrong with my body? what am I doing wrong? As we open up the refrigerator and reach for something to eat we say to ourselves, is this why I am sick? Do I need to change my diet? Sometimes when a person is sick for far too long, every food is under question, and every food can be a Saint or a devil in one's eyes. PTSD can grow quickly when someone is not feeling well and that PTSD can center itself all around food. Don’t miss this livestream.

Information from this video is from my bestselling book - Cleanse To Heal: Healing Plans For Sufferers of Anxiety, Depression, Acne, Eczema, Lyme, Gut Problems, Brain Fog, Weight Issues, Migraines, Bloating, Vertigo, Psoriasis, Cysts, Fatigue, PCOS, Fibroids, UTI, Endometriosis & Autoimmune  -  GET YOUR COPY TODAY: https://amzn.to/38mezp6

video.title: Food Fear   Are Your Health Symptoms Giving You An Eating Disorder
video.description:
When we get health symptoms, many times we associate those symptoms with the foods we are eating. When a symptom comes we question why is this problem here now? What is wrong with my body? what am I doing wrong? As we open up the refrigerator and reach for something to eat we say to ourselves, is this why I am sick? Do I need to change my diet? Sometimes when a person is sick for far too long, every food is under question, and every food can be a Saint or a devil in one's eyes. PTSD can grow quickly when someone is not feeling well and that PTSD can center itself all around food. Don’t miss this livestream.

video.description:
Forty years ago, the world of chronic illness was small. People were sick, people were dying, but it was a different landscape compared to what we see around us today. The one out of a hundred who were truly struggling with unbearable pain, of all kinds with no answers had very few options and many lost their lives when it could have been so different. Lyme disease, chronic fatigue, skin conditions, Thyroid Disease, Multiple sclerosis, just to name a few, were taunting people with no way out. Illnesses were thriving because toxins and pathogens were living in people’s bodies, percolating and festering with no way of being drawn out. Toxins and poisons are holding people back today more than ever before—toxins that are in the way of people’s everyday lives, causing high-speed, Mach 1 conditions. Today we can walk into a library and take out a free book called Medical Medium Cleanse To Heal and we can find a cleanse inside this book called The 3:6:9 Cleanse and we can change the course of our health history like so many have already done before. • Discover why there has never been a more important time in history to cleanse than now.

video.title: MENTAL HEALTH & TOXIC HEAVY METALS
video.description:
2-DAY HEAVY METAL DETOX CLEANSE

Final Day of The Free Medical Medium Heavy Metal Detox Cleanse  This is a great opportunity to learn how so many people have responsibly removed toxic heavy metals from their environment and lives.

Don’t think you have toxic heavy metals inside your brain and body? The truth is we are all exposed to these heavy metals just by being on this planet and they build up over time and can cause serious health problems. It’s impossible to avoid all exposures because toxic heavy metals are in our air, water, soil, perfumes, colognes, air fresheners, pesticides, pharmaceuticals, utensils, and pots and pans–to name just a few. And whether you eat a plant-based diet or you eat animal products, there is some degree of toxic heavy metals in both the plants and animals on this earth, so we are all exposed. 

Toxic heavy metals are the cause or part of the cause of countless illnesses, symptoms, and conditions, including ADHD, autism, anxiety, depression, Alzheimer’s, dementia, memory loss, brain fog, focus and concentration issues, tremors, Parkinson’s, tics, spasms, insomnia, sleep issues, fatigue, MS, lupus, autoimmune disease, Lyme disease, eczema, psoriasis, scleroderma, vitiligo, and rosacea and more. Surprised? If you are new to Medical Medium books and information, you might not have been aware of just how troublesome these toxic heavy metals can be. Medical research and science don’t yet understand just how pernicious these metals are when it comes to causing chronic illnesses of many varieties.

video.title: Q&A on Neurological Symptoms and More
video.description:
The population is experiencing a neurological meltdown. Have you noticed how many people aren’t feeling good or even thinking straight? Everyone seems to have a brain disease starting, chronic illness everywhere and yet no where to go.

Café Gratitude x Medical Medium Collaboration Pop-Up Dinners

Registration will open TOMORROW for two events with Anthony William to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium menu items at Café Gratitude. Tickets are very limited!

If you don’t already get the Medical Medium Newsletter, you can sign up now on the MM website, link in profile. Then watch your inbox this week for an exciting subscriber-only launch opportunity to celebrate the Café Gratitude x Medical Medium Collaboration.

Medical Medium Newsletter: https://www.medicalmedium.com/medical-medium-newsletter

This October, Café Gratitude will host two pop-up dinners in the Los Angeles area to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium dishes on the menu. These events are a rare opportunity to meet Anthony William in a close-knit setting and enjoy a four-course meal compassionately crafted to be gluten free, nut free, soy free, oil free, and low in sodium.

Registration will launch sometime TOMORROW, Thursday September 19th. Watch your inbox for the announcement when the links to purchase tickets go live. 

Seats are limited to only 200 people total. We anticipate high demand, so be prepared to get your tickets before they sell out! Tickets will be first come, first served.

Join Anthony William, Medical Medium, for a first-of-its-kind experience to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium dishes on the Café Gratitude menu.

Larchmont Pop-Up Dinner
This event limited to 80 tickets

Date and time:
Tuesday, October, 22, 2024, 6 – 9 pm PDT

Location:
Café Gratitude, 639 North Larchmont Boulevard, Los Angeles, CA 90004

Venice Pop-Up Dinner
This event limited to 120 tickets

Date and time:
Wednesday, October 23, 2024, 6 – 9 pm PDT

Location:
Café Gratitude, 512 Rose Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90291

Both events will follow the same format: 

6 – 7 pm: Arrival, red carpet, and meet-and-greet photo opportunity with Anthony William

7 – 9 pm: Seated 4-course plant-based dinner

video.title: 016 Potato: The Nightshade Healer
video.description:
Potatoes have gotten a bad rap for far too long. In this episode, I uncover important truths about potatoes and debunk theories and misconceptions about this healing food. I reveal how potatoes have become the food to blame and why it is not a good idea to consume potatoes covered in cheese, sour cream, milk, butter, mayonnaise, oil, or lard, and blame the potato for weight gain, diabetes, and insulin resistance. You will learn the truth about rising A1C levels and why potatoes are not the cause. I explain how potatoes are an anti-viral food and can help with many health symptoms and conditions including lupus, multiple sclerosis (MS), rheumatoid arthritis, neurological Lyme disease, chronic fatigue syndrome (CFS), Reynaud’s syndrome, vertigo, POTS, endometriosis, PCOS, and fibroids. I reveal how the glucose in potatoes can strengthen the central nervous system and why potatoes are crucial for anxiety, depression, bipolar disorder, OCD, and anyone going through an emotional struggle or hardship. I explain how potatoes do not cause inflammation in the body. Discover why potatoes should not be feared because they’re a nightshade. Learn where you get the trace mineral zinc from in a potato. You will learn how potatoes affect the good and bad bacteria in the intestinal tract. Find out how potatoes can help with the aftereffects of food poisoning. I share valuable information about how potatoes can soothe the digestive tract and help to heal Crohn’s, colitis, IBS, celiac, ulcers, gastroparesis, esophageal spasms, cramping, bloating, and other digestive disorders. Listen as I share the best ways to incorporate more potatoes into your diet and use this incredible food to aide in healing many health symptoms and conditions. 

To learn more, visit medicalmedium.com

video.title: Medical Medium's Nighttime Routine
video.description:
I went live to share my current nighttime routine with you. I get asked every day about what I eat and what I do to take care of myself and maintain so much energy when I work so many hours. I work seven days a week, 15 to 22 hours a day, writing the Medical Medium book series and getting healing information out to you in as many ways as possible so that you and your loved ones can heal. I don’t have time for a lot of self-care, but what I am able to do is take specific supplements and feed my body healing foods that support health and energy.

Each of the healing tools and supplements I discussed in the lives offer different benefits. You can find all of these supplements and more on the Supplement Directory on my website or at the links below. I want to give Vimergy as much support as possible so I am working with them to help spread the word so that more people can hopefully find these amazing supplements.

I noticed Vimergy currently has a new discount offer available also where you can save anywhere from 5 to 20% off, which you can read about on their website Vimergy.com

Medical Medium Nighttime Routine Supplements

Goldenseal – One of my favorite herbs, I use goldenseal periodically throughout the year. Vimergy Goldenseal is USDA organic, like all of their liquid extracts, and contains no alcohol, citric acid, soy, or corn. Find my favorite Goldenseal here: https://bit.ly/3BgT2yf

Cat’s Claw – An amazing option for immune support that I’ve been talking about for decades. This is a 10:1 extract that uses organic 100% flax glycerin (as do all the Vimergy extracts), which in my opinion is superior to so many glycerins used in the extract world. Find my favorite Cat’s Claw here: https://bit.ly/3xssKIf

Licorice – Another favorite herb that I recommend to friends and family and personally take myself. A little goes a long way. This is one of my go-to herbs for our health on this planet today. Find my favorite Licorice here: https://bit.ly/3RM87yP

Lemon Balm – Lemon Balm, otherwise called Melissa, is such a special and amazing herb. Melissa is like a best friend you can lean on when you need soothing and calming when things are busy or chaotic or hard. I love to take lemon balm daily for its calming qualities that help when you’re overworking or stressed. Find my favorite Lemon Balm here: https://bit.ly/3xkRYZ2

Nettle – Nettle is an immune-supporting herb I have taken for decades. From picking stinging nettle as a child to using the far more convenient extract form as an adult, it’s been a steady companion over my life. Find my favorite Nettle here: https://bit.ly/3xnYQF7

Micro-C – This star antioxidant is a vital nutrient we all need in one form or another. Micro-C is my preferred vitamin C product available at this time because it’s buffered vitamin C, which means it’s not as acidic as other forms of vitamin C like ascorbic acid. video.title: 041 Food Wars: What Side Are You On?
video.description:
Food belief systems run deep—they can be passed down from generation to generation. For some families, it can be hundreds of years and the food choices, food habits, food methods, food growing, food making is an entire food culture that becomes the fabric of the family foundation for lifetimes.

In the end, food means everything. Without it, we will not exist.

Recently in our present day history, food and health have collided, along with Social Media, and both food and food belief systems have become weaponized, and science has become the gun.

There are now two sides of the aisle when it comes to food belief systems, and within these two sides, there are many variations, but yet at the same time there are two main belief systems that have been battling each other. Now more than ever before these two main core belief systems have been ruthless in its pursuit to push people into confusion and fear. The two sides of the aisle are the Plant Based Vegan movement and the Animal Protein Based movement. For many, they both are saturated in strong beliefs and conviction, and both will defend itself with any kind of supportive science that’s available, even if that science in itself is lacking supportive evidence.

Food Wars can even be subliminal and not so forth coming, but instead somewhat stealth, and can persuade others that what they are doing for themselves is not as fruitful as they are told or believe. Meanwhile both sides of the aisle have more in common than anyone thinks.

Don’t miss this enlightening episode of the Medical Medium podcast—Food Wars: What Side Are You On?

For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com

The two sides of the aisle are the Plant Based Vegan movement and the Animal Protein Based movement. For many, they both are saturated in strong beliefs and conviction, and both will defend itself with any kind of supportive science that’s available, even if that science in itself is lacking supportive evidence.

Food Wars can even be subliminal and not so forth coming, but instead somewhat stealth, and can persuade others that what they are doing for themselves is not as fruitful as they are told or believe. Meanwhile both sides of the aisle have more in common than anyone thinks.

Don’t miss this enlightening episode of the Medical Medium podcast—Food Wars: What Side Are You On?

matches_found.targetFile: 029 Eating & Confused Trying To Use Food To Heal_jwdnltN8WM0_en_auto_summary.txt

video.title: 029 Eating & Confused: Trying To Use Food To Heal
video.description:
Do we listen to our body? Or are we just listening to our consciousness? Is our consciousness conditioned to choose the foods our body doesn’t want to eat? Does our body want the same foods our consciousness wants? No one should be judged upon what they are eating. In today’s harsh world it’s easy to lean on comfort foods and use them as a drug to get by. At the same time, we kind of are aware that our body really doesn’t want ice cream, chicken fingers, cheesy pasta, cheeseburgers, pizza, and chocolate. And what about our stomachs, do our stomachs want the same choices of food we want? Do our stomachs want beer and barbecue, chicken wings, cakes and cookies, donuts, macaroni and cheese, crab cakes and tuna fish sandwiches? Do our stomachs understand the term moderation and what our brainwashed conception of moderation is?
Let’s face it, there is a huge disconnect between our mind and body, and many people go through life believing that their body is telling them what it really wants when it comes to food and drink. People often think about what they need, but don’t realize it may not be what their stomach or body needs, and yet their stomach and body have no option but to live with the choices of the mind and consciousness of that person. Even then, that person’s choice in food may be what they are told to choose, especially by others in the realm of health, who are also recommending foods they think the body needs, and they themselves are in the same situation as the people they are recommending to. Everyone is stuck in a cycle of not knowing what their body wants or needs. Listen to this gripping episode about our digestion and how food works inside of our gut.

video.title: 039 Microdosing & Psychedelics: What Goes Wrong
video.description:
When we hear the words Micro-Dosing, a trending term, something happens in our mind: it draws a person in, it’s mysterious yet sounds scientific. The word “dose” holds power—it’s a word that has its own energetic force as if it’s alive. How is it alive? It’s an old word that the pharmaceutical world adopted, and the word is etched into generations of people. It’s instilled deep within the consciousness of the human mind and soul.

Around the word dose, there is fear. Fear stems from taking too much of something that isn’t normally good for us and even could be dangerous to us. A large dose of anything can be scary and even concerning. This is why prescription drugs have strict guidelines from medical authorities. Too big of a dose of a drug could mean overdosing, which is also a word deep in the consciousness of so many.

There is a party culture out there in this world. It’s a mindset that’s also ingrained in so many. Many people believe they need a stimulant of some kind to power them through life, or they feel they need something to relax them, and many people are struggling with symptoms and conditions, and are even suffering greatly with both mental and physical pain, so drinking and taking recreational drugs are on the rise. It’s unhealthy and toxic to the physical body and brain and has injured millions of people in various ways. Someone always knows someone that eventually had a close call or experience that wasn’t pleasing.

Microdosing has become a trend due to its seemingly controlled nature, an illusion that whatever you are partaking in is safe and even scientifically monitored in some way. It’s a way to lower fear and drive interest because how can something be toxic to you if it’s in such a small dosage. 

Get ready for a truly informative and enlightening episode—the truth about Microdosing.

For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com

video.title: ANXIOUS, OVERWHELMED & NERVOUSNESS
video.description:
Episode 14  of the Medical Medium Podcast 

ANXIETY – THEY SAY IT'S ALL IN YOUR HEAD Listen Here :  https://apple.co/2TxTT8k

Anxiety has many causes and triggers and can be different for everyone. Someone may have a sense of discomfort, unease, feeling no desire to keep moving, not wanting to ever be still, difficulty around crowds, feeling of nervousness, sweaty palms, or the inability to fall asleep easily because of racing thoughts. Another person could be on the bathroom floor, unable to move, body feeling numb, while trying to breathe into a paper bag. The range of anxiety isn’t 1 to 10, it’s more like 1 to 100,000, because that is how many variations of anxiety exist and how everyone can feel it differently. The symptoms of anxiety can range from mild to moderate to severe, and unless you’ve been in someone’s shoes who has struggled or suffered with anxiety, can you really understand what they’re going through.

In this episode, I reveal the ten most common triggers for anxiety and how to avoid them. I describe how emotional struggles, hardships, and emotional stress can be both a trigger and a cause for anxiety, and how this can affect the emotional center of the brain. I explain how anxiety can relate to an existing health symptom or condition. Learn more about how toxic heavy metals can play a role in having anxiety. Find out which fruits, leafy greens, herbs, wild foods, and vegetables are really helpful when healing anxiety, and which foods can be harmful and are best to avoid. Listen as I share specific healing tools that can help manage, control, and heal anxiety.

Many people have to live their life around anxiety. Anxiety can rule their every waking moment, and can determine what they’re going to be able to accomplish in a day, and leave someone feeling hopeless. Very little about anxiety is understood to this day; but in this episode, you can learn the true causes of anxiety, and tools that can help you head into a direction of healing and putting anxiety behind you forever.

video.title: ANXIOUS, OVERWHELMED & NERVOUSNESS
video.description:
Episode 14  of the Medical Medium Podcast 

ANXIETY – THEY SAY IT'S ALL IN YOUR HEAD Listen Here :  https://apple.co/2TxTT8k

Anxiety has many causes and triggers and can be different for everyone. Someone may have a sense of discomfort, unease, feeling no desire to keep moving, not wanting to ever be still, difficulty around crowds, feeling of nervousness, sweaty palms, or the inability to fall asleep easily because of racing thoughts. Another person could be on the bathroom floor, unable to move, body feeling numb, while trying to breathe into a paper bag. The range of anxiety isn’t 1 to 10, it’s more like 1 to 100,000, because that is how many variations of anxiety exist and how everyone can feel it differently. The symptoms of anxiety can range from mild to moderate to severe, and unless you’ve been in someone’s shoes who has struggled or suffered with anxiety, can you really understand what they’re going through.

In this episode, I reveal the ten most common triggers for anxiety and how to avoid them. I describe how emotional struggles, hardships, and emotional stress can be both a trigger and a cause for anxiety, and how this can affect the emotional center of the brain. I explain how anxiety can relate to an existing health symptom or condition. Learn more about how toxic heavy metals can play a role in having anxiety. Find out which fruits, leafy greens, herbs, wild foods, and vegetables are really helpful when healing anxiety, and which foods can be harmful and are best to avoid. Listen as I share specific healing tools that can help manage, control, and heal anxiety.

Many people have to live their life around anxiety. Anxiety can rule their every waking moment, and can determine what they’re going to be able to accomplish in a day, and leave someone feeling hopeless. Very little about anxiety is understood to this day; but in this episode, you can learn the true causes of anxiety, and tools that can help you head into a direction of healing and putting anxiety behind you forever.

video.title: B12 For Your Brain, Soul & Intuition
video.description:
Join me live to discover why B12 is such an important nutrient, not only for our brains and physical wellbeing, but emotionally and spiritually too. memory, mood, heart, energy, and more, but there is so much more to understand about how this special vitamin works with our soul to ignite our intuitive, psychic, telepathic, and clairvoyant skills. This is what I’ll be talking about on today’s live, plus so much more. 

When it comes to B12, it’s important to know that not every B12 supplement is helpful. In truth, many B12 supplements contain ingredients I don’t recommend, like citric acid or natural and artificial flavors. Then there’s the form of B12 a supplement offers. They aren’t all the same. For example, many B12 supplements contain cyanocobalamin, which is a form of B12 I don’t recommend.

My preferred form of B12 is a blend of methycobalamin and adenosylcobalamin. Vimergy B12 is my favorite B12 supplement because it contains the right kinds of B12, with the right quality, proportions, and clean ingredients–there’s no citric acid, alcohol, artificial flavors, natural flavors, low-quality glycerin, corn, soy, gluten or GMOs. I fully endorse Vimergy supplements because I love the quality, cleanliness, and efficacy of their products. I am working with Vimergy because it’s so important to get truly beneficial supplements out to the people who need them. I consider Vimergy Organic B12 to be a foundational supplement and I personally take it every day. 

My Favorite B12 : https://bit.ly/3xoGT9z

video.title: 018 Blood Draw: Bloodletting & Vampirism
video.description:
Many people battling symptoms, conditions, or chronic illness are subjected to routine blood draws and tests. How can these routine blood draws affect the body? 

In this episode, I uncover important truths about blood draws and reveal why the blood testing and donation system is broken and outdated. I explain how blood testing affects the immune system and why this can be dangerous, especially for the chronically ill. Find out how to determine the amount needed when getting your blood drawn and tested, and learn how much of your blood is discarded and wasted, and how very little of your blood is used for the testing process. Listen as I share what variables should be considered before getting a blood test and how gender can affect these variables. I cover what to ask for from your doctor when it comes to getting your blood tested and how best to protect yourself before and after a blood draw or blood donation.

To learn more, visit medicalmedium.com

video.title: 070 Problematic & Damaging Supplements: Deer Antler, Diatomaceous Earth, Essential Oils & More
video.description:
Everyone believes in essential oils as being helpful in some ways. This is true; essential oils can be helpful, but used in the wrong way can do the opposite. This is just one of the many supplements that people use on a daily basis that can have a negative impact on one’s health. Diatomaceous Earth has gained popularity as a fix-all for many problems related to health, but there is a dark side to that as well. So many are desperate for a quick fix that they run to any trend that gets placed before them. It’s a bear-eats-bear world of selling off anything and everything as a miracle fix for today’s problems. And then there are Creature Parts—they have become more popular than ever lately. Consuming a number of Creature Parts is also gaining steam because people still, to this day, think they can fix an organ by eating an organ. Get ready for this episode—you won’t be disappointed. We are covering some of the most deceiving trick-outs in the health industry.

Listen to this advertisement-free podcast on Apple & Spotify.

In this episode…
• Discover what you’re ingesting that could be harmful to your health.
• Learn what Creature Parts are and how can they be purposefully misleading.
• Learn about collagen, whale meat, colostrum and other supplements and what impact these can have upon ingestion.
• Uncover how the hormones in deer antler affect your body and your own hormones.
• Discover in what ways Diatomaceous Earth can be a trigger.
• Uncover the truth about digestive bitters and how it’s not so different from consuming alcohol.
• Learn what specific symptoms can be associated with a sensitive central nervous system and how Essential Oils can impact this.

All this and more, tune in and don’t miss out on this important episode. You can revisit this episode anytime you need it.

For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com

video.title: Café Gratitude x Medical Medium - New Menu Items Available Now
video.description:
This is a special moment for me because of what it means for you. Café Gratitude x Medical Medium dishes are now on the menu at both of the Café Gratitude locations in the Los Angeles area. Anyone who has applied Medical Medium information in their life knows what a challenge dining out can be. Navigating a restaurant menu when you’re working hard to heal can feel overwhelming and dispiriting. It’s easy to feel left out, tempted by what everyone else is ordering, and disappointed when you see what comes out on your plate—especially when you know how nourishing and delicious the healing foods you make in your own kitchen are. That’s why I’m beyond excited that you’ll now be able to order from a selection of gluten-free, nut-free, soy-free, oil-free, and low-sodium Medical Medium menu items at Café Gratitude. Whether you’re dining in or ordering takeout, you’ll get to treat yourself to elevated dishes designed around the life-changing foods, without ingredients to derail your healing. I’ve been blown away by the creativity and kindness of Chef Dreux and the rest of the Café Gratitude team, and I can’t wait for you to be a part of it.

View the menu here: https://cafegratitude.com/pages/cafe-gratitude-menus

video.title: Café Gratitude x Medical Medium - New Menu Items Available Now
video.description:
This is a special moment for me because of what it means for you. Café Gratitude x Medical Medium dishes are now on the menu at both of the Café Gratitude locations in the Los Angeles area. Anyone who has applied Medical Medium information in their life knows what a challenge dining out can be. Navigating a restaurant menu when you’re working hard to heal can feel overwhelming and dispiriting. It’s easy to feel left out, tempted by what everyone else is ordering, and disappointed when you see what comes out on your plate—especially when you know how nourishing and delicious the healing foods you make in your own kitchen are. That’s why I’m beyond excited that you’ll now be able to order from a selection of gluten-free, nut-free, soy-free, oil-free, and low-sodium Medical Medium menu items at Café Gratitude. Whether you’re dining in or ordering takeout, you’ll get to treat yourself to elevated dishes designed around the life-changing foods, without ingredients to derail your healing. I’ve been blown away by the creativity and kindness of Chef Dreux and the rest of the Café Gratitude team, and I can’t wait for you to be a part of it.

View the menu here: https://cafegratitude.com/pages/cafe-gratitude-menus

video.title: Food Fear   Are Your Health Symptoms Giving You An Eating Disorder
video.description:
When we get health symptoms, many times we associate those symptoms with the foods we are eating. When a symptom comes we question why is this problem here now? What is wrong with my body? what am I doing wrong? As we open up the refrigerator and reach for something to eat we say to ourselves, is this why I am sick? Do I need to change my diet? Sometimes when a person is sick for far too long, every food is under question, and every food can be a Saint or a devil in one's eyes. PTSD can grow quickly when someone is not feeling well and that PTSD can center itself all around food. Don’t miss this livestream.

Information from this video is from my bestselling book - Cleanse To Heal: Healing Plans For Sufferers of Anxiety, Depression, Acne, Eczema, Lyme, Gut Problems, Brain Fog, Weight Issues, Migraines, Bloating, Vertigo, Psoriasis, Cysts, Fatigue, PCOS, Fibroids, UTI, Endometriosis & Autoimmune  -  GET YOUR COPY TODAY: https://amzn.to/38mezp6

video.description:
Forty years ago, the world of chronic illness was small. People were sick, people were dying, but it was a different landscape compared to what we see around us today. The one out of a hundred who were truly struggling with unbearable pain, of all kinds with no answers had very few options and many lost their lives when it could have been so different. Lyme disease, chronic fatigue, skin conditions, Thyroid Disease, Multiple sclerosis, just to name a few, were taunting people with no way out. Illnesses were thriving because toxins and pathogens were living in people’s bodies, percolating and festering with no way of being drawn out. Toxins and poisons are holding people back today more than ever before—toxins that are in the way of people’s everyday lives, causing high-speed, Mach 1 conditions. Today we can walk into a library and take out a free book called Medical Medium Cleanse To Heal and we can find a cleanse inside this book called The 3:6:9 Cleanse and we can change the course of our health history like so many have already done before. The 3:6:9 Cleanse is a legendary cleanse that can change your life forever. Bold words?... Special words from so many who got their lives back and rose out of the ashes of chronic illness.

In this episode…
• Discover why there has never been a more important time in history to cleanse than now.
• Learn how The 3:6:9 Cleanse has saved thousands of lives and taken people out of wheelchairs.
• Uncover the truth behind the manufacturing of viruses and the dropping of chemicals from the sky.
• Learn why it is that the more toxins we have in our body, the more our immune system struggles and weakens.
• Discover the laundry list of things that are making us so toxic and how it just scratches the surface.
• Uncover the difference between surface detoxing and deep cleansing.
• Learn why cleanses can’t just be cleansing, and why they have to be nourishing in the sense that they are wired to repair a damaged, sensitive nervous system.
• Discover how The 3:6:9 Cleanse protects the brain from atrophy, unlike water fasting or other cleanses.
• Uncover the side-effects of fat-based cleanses or a no-glucose diet, and why sugar is vital to the brain.

All this and more, tune in and don’t miss out on this important episode. You can revisit this episode anytime you need it.

The truth is we are all exposed to these heavy metals just by being on this planet and they build up over time and can cause serious health problems. It’s impossible to avoid all exposures because toxic heavy metals are in our air, water, soil, perfumes, colognes, air fresheners, pesticides, pharmaceuticals, utensils, and pots and pans–to name just a few. video.title: Q&A on Neurological Symptoms and More
video.description:
The population is experiencing a neurological meltdown. Have you noticed how many people aren’t feeling good or even thinking straight? Everyone seems to have a brain disease starting, chronic illness everywhere and yet no where to go.

Café Gratitude x Medical Medium Collaboration Pop-Up Dinners

Registration will open TOMORROW for two events with Anthony William to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium menu items at Café Gratitude. Tickets are very limited!

If you don’t already get the Medical Medium Newsletter, you can sign up now on the MM website, link in profile. Then watch your inbox this week for an exciting subscriber-only launch opportunity to celebrate the Café Gratitude x Medical Medium Collaboration.

Medical Medium Newsletter: https://www.medicalmedium.com/medical-medium-newsletter

This October, Café Gratitude will host two pop-up dinners in the Los Angeles area to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium dishes on the menu. These events are a rare opportunity to meet Anthony William in a close-knit setting and enjoy a four-course meal compassionately crafted to be gluten free, nut free, soy free, oil free, and low in sodium.

Registration will launch sometime TOMORROW, Thursday September 19th. Watch your inbox for the announcement when the links to purchase tickets go live. 

Seats are limited to only 200 people total. We anticipate high demand, so be prepared to get your tickets before they sell out! Tickets will be first come, first served.

Join Anthony William, Medical Medium, for a first-of-its-kind experience to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium dishes on the Café Gratitude menu.

Larchmont Pop-Up Dinner
This event limited to 80 tickets

Date and time:
Tuesday, October, 22, 2024, 6 – 9 pm PDT

Location:
Café Gratitude, 639 North Larchmont Boulevard, Los Angeles, CA 90004

Venice Pop-Up Dinner
This event limited to 120 tickets

Date and time:
Wednesday, October 23, 2024, 6 – 9 pm PDT

Location:
Café Gratitude, 512 Rose Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90291

Both events will follow the same format: 

6 – 7 pm: Arrival, red carpet, and meet-and-greet photo opportunity with Anthony William

7 – 9 pm: Seated 4-course plant-based dinner

Café Gratitude will sell the event tickets for the cost of each dinner. No proceeds will go to Medical Medium.

Don’t worry if you can’t make it to one of the pop-up dinners. You’ll still be able to order Medical Medium dishes at Café Gratitude whenever you’re in the Los Angeles area. Stay tuned for the announcement when Medical Medium menu items launch in mid-October! 

Medical Medium Podcast: https://bit.ly/3Loe5oV

video.title: 016 Potato: The Nightshade Healer
video.description:
Potatoes have gotten a bad rap for far too long. In this episode, I uncover important truths about potatoes and debunk theories and misconceptions about this healing food. I reveal how potatoes have become the food to blame and why it is not a good idea to consume potatoes covered in cheese, sour cream, milk, butter, mayonnaise, oil, or lard, and blame the potato for weight gain, diabetes, and insulin resistance. You will learn the truth about rising A1C levels and why potatoes are not the cause. I explain how potatoes are an anti-viral food and can help with many health symptoms and conditions including lupus, multiple sclerosis (MS), rheumatoid arthritis, neurological Lyme disease, chronic fatigue syndrome (CFS), Reynaud’s syndrome, vertigo, POTS, endometriosis, PCOS, and fibroids. I reveal how the glucose in potatoes can strengthen the central nervous system and why potatoes are crucial for anxiety, depression, bipolar disorder, OCD, and anyone going through an emotional struggle or hardship. I explain how potatoes do not cause inflammation in the body. Discover why potatoes should not be feared because they’re a nightshade. Learn where you get the trace mineral zinc from in a potato. You will learn how potatoes affect the good and bad bacteria in the intestinal tract. Find out how potatoes can help with the aftereffects of food poisoning. I share valuable information about how potatoes can soothe the digestive tract and help to heal Crohn’s, colitis, IBS, celiac, ulcers, gastroparesis, esophageal spasms, cramping, bloating, and other digestive disorders. Listen as I share the best ways to incorporate more potatoes into your diet and use this incredible food to aide in healing many health symptoms and conditions. 

To learn more, visit medicalmedium.com

video.description:
The population is experiencing a neurological meltdown. Have you noticed how many people aren’t feeling good or even thinking straight? Everyone seems to have a brain disease starting, chronic illness everywhere and yet no where to go.

Café Gratitude x Medical Medium Collaboration Pop-Up Dinners

Registration will open TOMORROW for two events with Anthony William to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium menu items at Café Gratitude. Tickets are very limited!

If you don’t already get the Medical Medium Newsletter, you can sign up now on the MM website, link in profile. Then watch your inbox this week for an exciting subscriber-only launch opportunity to celebrate the Café Gratitude x Medical Medium Collaboration.

Medical Medium Newsletter: https://www.medicalmedium.com/medical-medium-newsletter

This October, Café Gratitude will host two pop-up dinners in the Los Angeles area to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium dishes on the menu. These events are a rare opportunity to meet Anthony William in a close-knit setting and enjoy a four-course meal compassionately crafted to be gluten free, nut free, soy free, oil free, and low in sodium.

Registration will launch sometime TOMORROW, Thursday September 19th. Watch your inbox for the announcement when the links to purchase tickets go live. 

Seats are limited to only 200 people total. We anticipate high demand, so be prepared to get your tickets before they sell out! Tickets will be first come, first served.

Join Anthony William, Medical Medium, for a first-of-its-kind experience to celebrate the launch of Medical Medium dishes on the Café Gratitude menu.

Larchmont Pop-Up Dinner
This event limited to 80 tickets

Date and time:
Tuesday, October, 22, 2024, 6 – 9 pm PDT

Location:
Café Gratitude, 639 North Larchmont Boulevard, Los Angeles, CA 90004

Venice Pop-Up Dinner
This event limited to 120 tickets

Both events will follow the same format: 

6 – 7 pm: Arrival, red carpet, and meet-and-greet photo opportunity with Anthony William

7 – 9 pm: Seated 4-course plant-based dinner

Café Gratitude will sell the event tickets for the cost of each dinner. No proceeds will go to Medical Medium.

Don’t worry if you can’t make it to one of the pop-up dinners. You’ll still be able to order Medical Medium dishes at Café Gratitude whenever you’re in the Los Angeles area. Stay tuned for the announcement when Medical Medium menu items launch in mid-October!

video.title: Medical Medium's Nighttime Routine
video.description:
I went live to share my current nighttime routine with you. I get asked every day about what I eat and what I do to take care of myself and maintain so much energy when I work so many hours. I work seven days a week, 15 to 22 hours a day, writing the Medical Medium book series and getting healing information out to you in as many ways as possible so that you and your loved ones can heal. I don’t have time for a lot of self-care, but what I am able to do is take specific supplements and feed my body healing foods that support health and energy.

Each of the healing tools and supplements I discussed in the lives offer different benefits. You can find all of these supplements and more on the Supplement Directory on my website or at the links below. I want to give Vimergy as much support as possible so I am working with them to help spread the word so that more people can hopefully find these amazing supplements.

I noticed Vimergy currently has a new discount offer available also where you can save anywhere from 5 to 20% off, which you can read about on their website Vimergy.com

Medical Medium Nighttime Routine Supplements

Goldenseal – One of my favorite herbs, I use goldenseal periodically throughout the year. Vimergy Goldenseal is USDA organic, like all of their liquid extracts, and contains no alcohol, citric acid, soy, or corn. Find my favorite Goldenseal here: https://bit.ly/3BgT2yf

Cat’s Claw – An amazing option for immune support that I’ve been talking about for decades. This is a 10:1 extract that uses organic 100% flax glycerin (as do all the Vimergy extracts), which in my opinion is superior to so many glycerins used in the extract world. Find my favorite Cat’s Claw here: https://bit.ly/3xssKIf

Licorice – Another favorite herb that I recommend to friends and family and personally take myself. A little goes a long way. This is one of my go-to herbs for our health on this planet today. Find my favorite Licorice here: https://bit.ly/3RM87yP

Lemon Balm – Lemon Balm, otherwise called Melissa, is such a special and amazing herb. Melissa is like a best friend you can lean on when you need soothing and calming when things are busy or chaotic or hard. I love to take lemon balm daily for its calming qualities that help when you’re overworking or stressed. Find my favorite Lemon Balm here: https://bit.ly/3xkRYZ2

Nettle – Nettle is an immune-supporting herb I have taken for decades. From picking stinging nettle as a child to using the far more convenient extract form as an adult, it’s been a steady companion over my life. Find my favorite Nettle here: https://bit.ly/3xnYQF7

Micro-C – This star antioxidant is a vital nutrient we all need in one form or another. Micro-C is my preferred vitamin C product available at this time because it’s buffered vitamin C, which means it’s not as acidic as other forms of vitamin C like ascorbic acid. Find my favorite Micro-C here: https://bit.ly/3U5udy5

Zinc Sulfate – Zinc is an essential mineral, which means we all need it in some form, much like vitamin C, and also supports a healthy immune system. Vimergy’s Zinc Sulfate doesn’t contain citric acid, alcohol, or natural and artificial flavors. Find my favorite Zinc Sulfate here: https://bit.ly/3eEel59

B12 – This liquid B12 has my preferred blend of adenosylcobalamin and methylcobalamin, two bioavailable and important forms of B12, in the proportions that I personally like. Find my favorite B12 here: https://bit.ly/3xoGT9z 

Curcumin with Turmeric – These liquid capsules contain both curcumin, which is the active compound in turmeric, plus wholefood turmeric. There’s also no black pepper in this formula, which is important to me because black pepper can be extremely irritating for many people who have gut problems. Find my favorite Curcumin with Turmeric here: https://bit.ly/3U7mzmG

Magnesium Glycinate – I love that this Magnesium Glycinate also contains organic turmeric and organic ginger. Magnesium plays an important role in normal neurological function, helps the muscles, heart, cells, and more. Find my favorite Magnesium Glycinate here: https://bit.ly/3BegQ5P

GABA – This supports me with responding well to stress and overwork and is a favorite supplement for me. GABA helps the nervous system. I love that this GABA comes with magnesium glycinate for additional benefits. Find my favorite GABA here: https://bit.ly/3xo8kQS

PropolisPure – One of my favorite supplements of all time and one I take the most for immune support overall. It’s so difficult to find a clean propolis, and this one is. Vimergy’s PropolisPure contains propolis sourced from a limited number of carefully screened beekeeping operations. Find my favorite PropolisPure here: https://bit.ly/3Lm4YDx

Melatonin – An incredible sleep aid, for one. I personally take my melatonin right before I go to sleep, not an hour or two before bedtime. Find my favorite Melatonin here: https://bit.ly/3Duie79

Love and many blessings.

Licorice – Another favorite herb that I recommend to friends and family and personally take myself. A little goes a long way. This is one of my go-to herbs for our health on this planet today. Find my favorite Licorice here: https://bit.ly/3RM87yP

Lemon Balm – Lemon Balm, otherwise called Melissa, is such a special and amazing herb. Melissa is like a best friend you can lean on when you need soothing and calming when things are busy or chaotic or hard. I love to take lemon balm daily for its calming qualities that help when you’re overworking or stressed. Find my favorite Lemon Balm here: https://bit.ly/3xkRYZ2

Nettle – Nettle is an immune-supporting herb I have taken for decades. From picking stinging nettle as a child to using the far more convenient extract form as an adult, it’s been a steady companion over my life. Find my favorite Nettle here: https://bit.ly/3xnYQF7

Micro-C – This star antioxidant is a vital nutrient we all need in one form or another. Micro-C is my preferred vitamin C product available at this time because it’s buffered vitamin C, which means it’s not as acidic as other forms of vitamin C like ascorbic acid. Find my favorite Micro-C here: https://bit.ly/3U5udy5

Zinc Sulfate – Zinc is an essential mineral, which means we all need it in some form, much like vitamin C, and also supports a healthy immune system. Vimergy’s Zinc Sulfate doesn’t contain citric acid, alcohol, or natural and artificial flavors. Find my favorite Zinc Sulfate here: https://bit.ly/3eEel59

B12 – This liquid B12 has my preferred blend of adenosylcobalamin and methylcobalamin, two bioavailable and important forms of B12, in the proportions that I personally like. Find my favorite B12 here: https://bit.ly/3xoGT9z 

Curcumin with Turmeric – These liquid capsules contain both curcumin, which is the active compound in turmeric, plus wholefood turmeric. There’s also no black pepper in this formula, which is important to me because black pepper can be extremely irritating for many people who have gut problems. Find my favorite Curcumin with Turmeric here: https://bit.ly/3U7mzmG

Magnesium Glycinate – I love that this Magnesium Glycinate also contains organic turmeric and organic ginger. Magnesium plays an important role in normal neurological function, helps the muscles, heart, cells, and more. Find my favorite Magnesium Glycinate here: https://bit.ly/3BegQ5P

GABA – This supports me with responding well to stress and overwork and is a favorite supplement for me. GABA helps the nervous system. I love that this GABA comes with magnesium glycinate for additional benefits. Find my favorite GABA here: https://bit.ly/3xo8kQS

PropolisPure – One of my favorite supplements of all time and one I take the most for immune support overall. It’s so difficult to find a clean propolis, and this one is. Vimergy’s PropolisPure contains propolis sourced from a limited number of carefully screened beekeeping operations. Find my favorite PropolisPure here: https://bit.ly/3Lm4YDx

Melatonin – An incredible sleep aid, for one. I personally take my melatonin right before I go to sleep, not an hour or two before bedtime. Find my favorite Melatonin here: https://bit.ly/3Duie79

Love and many blessings.

video.title: 041 Food Wars: What Side Are You On?
video.description:
Food belief systems run deep—they can be passed down from generation to generation. For some families, it can be hundreds of years and the food choices, food habits, food methods, food growing, food making is an entire food culture that becomes the fabric of the family foundation for lifetimes.

In the end, food means everything. Without it, we will not exist.

Recently in our present day history, food and health have collided, along with Social Media, and both food and food belief systems have become weaponized, and science has become the gun.

There are now two sides of the aisle when it comes to food belief systems, and within these two sides, there are many variations, but yet at the same time there are two main belief systems that have been battling each other. Now more than ever before these two main core belief systems have been ruthless in its pursuit to push people into confusion and fear. The two sides of the aisle are the Plant Based Vegan movement and the Animal Protein Based movement. For many, they both are saturated in strong beliefs and conviction, and both will defend itself with any kind of supportive science that’s available, even if that science in itself is lacking supportive evidence.

Food Wars can even be subliminal and not so forth coming, but instead somewhat stealth, and can persuade others that what they are doing for themselves is not as fruitful as they are told or believe. Meanwhile both sides of the aisle have more in common than anyone thinks.

Don’t miss this enlightening episode of the Medical Medium podcast—Food Wars: What Side Are You On?

For more information visit www.medicalmedium.com
